Check our vlog channel - YouTwoVLOGS - for the newest video.

a reminder of why I chose to be in the entertainment industry. 

I had the pleasure of attending the LA premiere of #theromantics and just the two episodes we watched ignited a new found inspiration for my craft. 

I grew up watching @yrf films with my parents every weekend, @smritimundhra brought all the nostalgia to the screen. definitely check it out on Netflix if you have a chance.

We just hit THREE MILLION subscribers and ONE BILLION views on our channel! So grateful for anyone who has ever supported us and stuck with us. My heart and soul is honestly filled with so much gratitude. Can’t wait to keep creating and growing and hopefully make you guys laugh. 💛
